### 基础测试 - 需要先获取有效的JWT token
# 注意：实际使用时需要先通过用户认证获取token

### 1. 创建手帐本
POST http://localhost:3000/note-books
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "我的第一个手帐本",
  "coverImg": "https://example.com/cover.jpg"
}

### 2. 获取手帐本列表
GET http://localhost:3000/note-books
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 3. 创建手帐
POST http://localhost:3000/notes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "noteBookId": "NOTEBOOK_ID_HERE",
  "title": "第一篇手帐",
  "content": "这是我的手帐内容...",
  "tags": ["日记", "生活"]
}

### 4. 获取手帐列表
GET http://localhost:3000/notes
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. 搜索手帐
GET http://localhost:3000/notes/search?q=手帐
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 6. 获取最近手帐
GET http://localhost:3000/notes/recent?limit=5
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 7. 获取用户统计
GET http://localhost:3000/stats/user
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 8. 获取标签统计
GET http://localhost:3000/stats/tags
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
